"ຕາຕະລາງ ແລະ ເວລາຫວ່າງຂອງທ່ານໃນ </span></font><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບ"
"ປະຕິທິນ</font><font class=\"text-black\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">"
".</span></font></strong>"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><span class=\"display-4-fs\">Odoo for Therapy "
"Practices</span></strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><span class=\"display-4-fs\">Odoo ສຳລັບການບໍລິການບຳບັດ</span></strong>"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A free, personalized, integrated<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> "
"Website </font></strong>in a few clicks. Get new leads or direct appointment"
" online in a few clicks."
msgstr ""
"ສ້າງ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> ເວັບໄຊ </font></strong> ທີ່ປັບແຕ່ງໄດ້ ແ"
"ລະ ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຄົບວົງຈອນໄດ້ໂດຍບໍ່ເສຍຄ່າພາຍໃນບໍ່ເທົ່າໃດຄລິກ. ຮັບລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່ໃໝ່ ຫຼື ຮັບການນັດໝາຍອອນລາຍໄດ້ໂດ"
"ຍກົງ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add an upfront payment in your Appointment Type."
msgstr "ເພີ່ມການຊຳລະເງິນລ່ວງໜ້າໃນປະເພດການນັດໝາຍຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add the Subscription App and invoice automatically based on a subscription "
"type."
msgstr "ເພີ່ມແອັບການສະໝັກສະມາຊິກ ແລະ ອອກໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດຕາມປະເພດການສະໝັກ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"After each appointment, an automatic email will be sent to suggest your "
"patient to already book its next appointment."
msgstr ""
"ຫຼັງຈາກການນັດໝາຍແຕ່ລະຄັ້ງ, ອີເມວອັດຕະໂນມັດຈະຖືກສົ່ງອອກເພື່ອແນະນຳໃຫ້ຄົນເຈັບຂອງທ່ານຈອງການນັດໝາຍຄັ້ງຕໍ່"
"ໄປ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"As you qualify Emily's needs, you update the lead status to \"Qualified\" in"
" the CRM pipeline."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອທ່ານກວດສອບຄວາມຕ້ອງການຂອງ Emily ແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດອັບເດດສະຖານະເປັນ \"ມີຄຸນສົມບັດ\" ໃນຂັ້ນຕ"
"ອນການຂາຍຂອງ CRM."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Auto-post your invoice on a regular basis."
msgstr "ລົງບັນຊີໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ຂອງທ່ານໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດເປັນປະຈຳ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Automated recurring invoicing with the <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Subscription App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"ການອອກໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ຊ້ຳແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດດ້ວຍ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບການສະໝັ"
"ກສະມາຊິກ</font></strong>."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Basics"
msgstr "ພື້ນຖານ"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Be careful, using the \"Log Note\" in your contact with be displayed only "
"for you and your eventual team. If you select the \"Send message\" option, "
"this will notify your customer (which can be really interesting also)."
msgstr ""
"ຂໍ້ຄວນລະວັງ, ການໃຊ້ \"ບັນທຶກຂໍ້ຄວາມ (Log Note)\" ໃນລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່ຈະສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນສະເພາະທ່ານ ແລະ "
"ທີມງານຂອງທ່ານເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ຫາກທ່ານເລືອກ \"ສົ່ງຂໍ້ຄວາມ (Send message)\", ມັນຈະແຈ້ງເຕືອນໄປຫາລູກຄ້າຂ"
"ອງທ່ານນຳ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model:mail.template,name:wellness_practitioner.booking_suggestion
msgid "Book your next appointment"
msgstr "ຈອງການນັດໝາຍຄັ້ງຕໍ່ໄປຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By installing this package, you'll have access to a range of essential apps,"
" including CRM, Appointment and Invoicing. Let's explore how these modules "
"can streamline your therapy practice operations."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອຕິດຕັ້ງແພັກເກດນີ້, ທ່ານຈະສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງແອັບທີ່ຈຳເປັນຕ່າງໆ ເຊັ່ນ: CRM, ການນັດໝາຍ ແລະ ການອອກໃບ"
"ແຈ້ງໜີ້. ມາເບິ່ງກັນວ່າໂມດູນເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ການດຳເນີນງານການບຳບັດຂອງທ່ານສະດວກຂຶ້ນຄືແນວໃດ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By uploading this module's demo data, your database has been filled with a "
"few contacts."
msgstr ""
"ໂດຍການໂຫລດຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງຂອງໂມດູນນີ້, ຖານຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານຈະຖືກເພີ່ມດ້ວຍລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່ບາງສ່ວນ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Discover more about Odoo by diving into our"
msgstr "ຄົ້ນຫາເພີ່ມເຕີມກ່ຽວກັບ Odoo ໂດຍການເຂົ້າໄປເບິ່ງ"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Do you want to go further?"
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໄປຕໍ່ໃຫ້ໄກກວ່ານີ້ບໍ່?"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Ease your invoicing process with the <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Invoice App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"ເຮັດໃຫ້ຂັ້ນຕອນການອອກໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ຂອງທ່ານງ່າຍຂຶ້ນດ້ວຍ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແ"
"ອັບໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້</font></strong>."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model:calendar.alarm,name:wellness_practitioner.alarm_mail_1
msgid "Follow up"
msgstr "ຕິດຕາມຜົນ"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Getting Started\n"
"            To begin, you'll find the key applications you need on your Odoo dashboard. Let's take a closer look at how you can use these tools."
msgstr ""
"ການເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ\n"
"            ເພື່ອເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ, ທ່ານຈະພົບເຫັນແອັບພລິເຄຊັນທີ່ຈຳເປັນໃນໜ້າແດຊບອດ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານ. ມາເບິ່ງລ"
"າຍລະອຽດກັນວ່າທ່ານຈະສາມາດໃຊ້ເຄື່ອງມືເຫຼົ່ານີ້ໄດ້ແນວໃດ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you navigate to the Invoice App, you can manage your invoices. You have "
"many possibilities to streamline your invoicing process:"
msgstr ""
"ຫາກທ່ານໄປທີ່ແອັບໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້, ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດການໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້. ທ່ານມີຫຼາຍທາງເລືອກທີ່ຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ຂັ້ນຕອນກ"
"ານອອກໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ສະດວກຂຶ້ນ:"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you open Emily's opportunity in your CRM, you can see in the Chatter (on "
"the right column) that she received an email from you with a call to action "
"to book an appointment."
msgstr ""
"ຫາກທ່ານເປີດໂອກາດຂອງ Emily ໃນ CRM, ທ່ານຈະເຫັນໃນຊ່ອງສົນທະນາ (Chatter - ຖັນເບື້ອງຂວາ) ວ່າລ"
"າວໄດ້ຮັບອີເມວຈາກທ່ານ ພ້ອມປຸ່ມສຳລັບການຈອງນັດໝາຍ."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to adapt your flow and set new automation rules, click the Gear "
"Icon in the top of a CRM column and select \"Automation\", or add automated "
"email in your Appointment Type."
msgstr ""
